    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nAfter updating to v0.12, I get this error:\n\n```\nE5113: Lua chunk: .../usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/lsp.lua:347: /home/user/.config/nvim/lsp/clangd.lua: not a table\nstack traceback:\n        [C]: in function 'error'\n        .../usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/lsp.lua:347: in function '__index'\n        .../usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/lsp.lua:618: in function 'enable'\n        .../home/user/.config/nvim/lua/user/lsp.lua:5: in main chunk\n        [C]: in function 'require'\n        /home/user/.config/nvim/init.lua:6: in main chunk\n```\n\nclangd.lua:\n```lua\nvim.lsp.config.clangd = {\n    cmd = { \"clangd\" },\n    filetypes = { 'c', \"cpp\" },\n    root_markers = { \"Makefile\" }\n}\n```\n\nI get the same error on Termux too.",
