            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Pleae read the documentation. This is not how lsp/ should be used.\n```lua\n  -- Defined in <rtp>/lsp/clangd.lua\n  return {\n    cmd = { 'clangd' },\n    root_markers = { '.clangd', 'compile_commands.json' },\n    filetypes = { 'c', 'cpp' },\n  }\n```",
